                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">GRIFFITHS—
<rs id="t18350302-675-verdict-4" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18350302-675-verdict-4" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
